WEBVTT

00:01.041 --> 00:05.000
[intriguing music]

00:09.791 --> 00:11.541
[lion roars]

00:24.416 --> 00:25.583
[paper scrunching]

00:25.666 --> 00:28.791
[blows thudding]
[tires screeching]

00:28.875 --> 00:31.833
[crate thuds]

00:31.916 --> 00:35.041
[neon lights humming]

00:36.666 --> 00:39.583
[intriguing synth music playing]

00:39.666 --> 00:42.250
[woman]
Inside every ballerina's heart,

00:42.958 --> 00:44.833
is the blood of a warrior.

00:53.291 --> 00:56.333
They turn pain into beauty...

00:59.541 --> 01:00.541
♪ Rhythm ♪

01:00.625 --> 01:03.458
[woman]
...chaos into precision...

01:03.541 --> 01:05.208
♪ Rhythm ♪

01:07.541 --> 01:09.500
♪ You can feel it, you can feel
it ♪

01:09.583 --> 01:11.791
[woman]
...their bodies into art.

01:14.875 --> 01:15.708
♪ Rhythm ♪

01:15.791 --> 01:20.541
[woman]
Sweat, blood, sacrifice...

01:20.625 --> 01:22.125
♪ Rhythm is a dancer ♪

01:22.208 --> 01:23.125
♪ Rhythm ♪

01:23.208 --> 01:25.916
[woman] But not everyone
achieves their dream.

01:28.083 --> 01:29.916
♪ Rhythm is a dancer ♪

01:30.000 --> 01:31.791
♪ It's a soul's companion ♪

01:31.875 --> 01:34.708
♪ You can feel it everywhere ♪

01:35.791 --> 01:37.500
♪ Lift your hands and voices ♪

01:37.583 --> 01:39.583
♪ Free your mind and join us ♪

01:39.666 --> 01:42.958
♪ You can feel it in the air ♪

01:43.041 --> 01:46.583
♪ Oh-Oh ♪
- [Princess] Miss Thorna,

01:46.666 --> 01:48.041
the showcase is in two days.

01:48.125 --> 01:49.958
If Bones doesn't take rehearsals
seriously,

01:50.041 --> 01:51.583
I should dance her part.

01:51.666 --> 01:54.166
- [Miss Thorna] Her bus
was late. She'll be here.

01:54.250 --> 01:56.583
- She's late 'cause her broke
ass can't afford a clock.

01:56.666 --> 01:58.541
- [Bones] Hm, sorry, my limo was
late, Princess.

02:00.291 --> 02:01.708
- Ah.

02:01.791 --> 02:03.166
- Are we gonna dance or what?

02:06.041 --> 02:07.083
- Okay.

02:07.166 --> 02:09.083
- Five, six, seven, eight.

02:09.166 --> 02:11.333
And one, two, three, four,
[bright classical music]

02:11.416 --> 02:13.333
five, six, and four more, eight.

02:13.416 --> 02:17.916
And one, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

02:18.000 --> 02:19.250
Stop.

02:19.875 --> 02:21.958
Right. Back to the soutenus,
quickly.

02:22.041 --> 02:23.083
What happened?

02:23.166 --> 02:24.333
Come on, Grace.

02:24.416 --> 02:26.541
Usual bullshit.

02:26.625 --> 02:27.875
Earth to Grace.

02:28.875 --> 02:30.208
Quickly, come on.

02:30.291 --> 02:31.791
Five, six, seven, eight,
[bright classical music]

02:31.875 --> 02:34.208
and one, two, three, four,

02:34.291 --> 02:35.833
five, six, seven, eight,

02:35.916 --> 02:38.041
and one, two, three, four,

02:38.125 --> 02:40.041
five, six, seven, eight.

02:40.125 --> 02:41.916
Remember you're on a flight
to Budapest tomorrow.

02:42.000 --> 02:43.833
So dance like your lives depend
on it.

02:43.916 --> 02:45.333
Solo.

02:45.416 --> 02:49.458
[Bones breathing deliberately]

02:49.541 --> 02:50.666
Stop.

02:51.416 --> 02:52.583
Come on.

02:52.666 --> 02:54.791
Princess, wait your turn.

02:55.750 --> 02:58.458
Right, and Chloe, you need
to trust your sister, right?

02:58.541 --> 02:59.541
She will cue you in.

02:59.625 --> 03:01.333
Seven, eight, and one

03:01.416 --> 03:03.458
two, three, four, five

03:03.541 --> 03:05.208
That's beautiful, Chloe.

03:05.291 --> 03:08.416
Remember teamwork. Everyone,
teamwork.

03:09.916 --> 03:14.791
And one, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight,

03:14.875 --> 03:18.833
and one, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight,

03:18.916 --> 03:20.583
and one, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight,

03:20.666 --> 03:22.541
[music builds]

03:22.625 --> 03:24.041
[music stops]
[Bones breathes heavily]

03:24.375 --> 03:25.916
Time, ladies.

03:27.166 --> 03:28.666
[dancers panting heavily]
Alright.

03:30.625 --> 03:32.166
- Hey, don't you know
how to fucking count?

03:34.166 --> 03:37.833
I'm talking to you. You
turned in sickle, bitch.

03:37.916 --> 03:39.083
[Princess gasps]
- Bones!

03:39.166 --> 03:40.458
If you want the solo, it's
yours.

03:40.541 --> 03:41.791
I quit.

03:41.875 --> 03:42.708
- [Princess] Miss
Thorna, did you see that?

03:42.791 --> 03:45.333
About time someone smacked that
bitch

03:45.416 --> 03:50.291
[door clicks open]
[music bleeds out]

03:53.291 --> 03:56.375
[siren wails nearby]

04:05.750 --> 04:07.041
- You shouldn't have hit her.

04:07.791 --> 04:08.916
- It was an accident.

04:10.750 --> 04:12.416
Her face slipped into my fist.

04:13.250 --> 04:15.666
- Well, her mother is sponsoring
you so you could compete.

04:15.750 --> 04:18.416
So, you know, maybe you show
a little bit of gratitude

04:18.500 --> 04:20.041
before you try and break her
nose.

04:20.791 --> 04:22.707
You know, what you've got to
understand is

04:22.791 --> 04:25.541
the Budapest Showcase
could change your life.

04:25.625 --> 04:27.166
- Ballet is a rich bitch sport.

04:28.541 --> 04:29.541
I keep telling you,

04:30.166 --> 04:31.166
I don't belong.

04:36.916 --> 04:38.916
["Gonna Make You Sweat:
Everybody Dance Now"]

04:39.000 --> 04:41.166
♪ Everybody dance now ♪

04:44.416 --> 04:47.207
[jet engines whining]

04:47.291 --> 04:48.416
[tire screeches]

04:48.500 --> 04:51.041
[bus engine revs]
♪ Give me the music ♪

04:52.750 --> 04:55.041
♪ Give me the music ♪

04:55.750 --> 04:57.541
♪ Everybody dance now ♪

05:03.125 --> 05:06.333
[bell chimes]
♪ Everybody dance now ♪

05:06.416 --> 05:08.041
- Mom, I'm sure you're sleeping,

05:08.125 --> 05:11.416
but we did land after being
rerouted.

05:12.625 --> 05:14.166
They put me on a bus, so like
pray for me.

05:15.791 --> 05:19.416
[bus chugging and rattling]

05:20.875 --> 05:22.875
♪ Everybody dance now ♪

05:24.541 --> 05:26.291
- [Princess] Can anyone smell
smoke?

05:27.041 --> 05:28.457
[engine stops]
[hydraulics hiss]

05:28.541 --> 05:29.916
- [Miss Thorna] It's all been a
bit of a nightmare.

05:30.000 --> 05:32.332
Our flight got diverted and
the airport lost our luggage

05:32.416 --> 05:33.541
and another bus is broken down.

05:33.625 --> 05:35.541
So, but no, I assure you my
dancers

05:35.625 --> 05:37.082
will be on that stage tomorrow.

05:37.166 --> 05:38.416
[tool clatters]
[driver mutters]

05:38.500 --> 05:40.125
But we are very much on route.

05:41.291 --> 05:43.166
Oh, no, no, no, no. Don't,
don't alter the program.

05:43.250 --> 05:44.582
No, no need, um...

05:44.666 --> 05:47.291
No, my dancers will definitely
be at the showcase.

05:48.375 --> 05:51.207
- Miss Thorna, the next town
is only two kilometers away.

05:51.291 --> 05:53.625
But my guidebook is saying-
- What did they say?

05:54.125 --> 05:56.582
- Well the artistic director
is very understanding

05:56.666 --> 05:57.791
of our situation.

05:58.666 --> 05:59.707
But...

05:59.791 --> 06:00.875
- They're looking into
alternates.

06:01.916 --> 06:04.541
- Yeah, I'm afraid they are.

06:05.625 --> 06:08.583
Girls, grab your ballet bags.
Come on.

06:08.666 --> 06:10.541
If we stay on this bus, we'll
never make the showcase.

06:13.166 --> 06:14.166
Right. Yes.

06:14.250 --> 06:15.916
[bird calls]

06:16.500 --> 06:18.457
All right?
- [Grace] Oh my God.

06:18.541 --> 06:21.082
There's just like so much
nature.

06:21.166 --> 06:24.125
[portentous music]

06:26.916 --> 06:28.957
May the wolves have
mercy on you

06:29.041 --> 06:32.666
[thunder rumbles]
[raindrops spatter]

06:33.625 --> 06:36.375
[thunder rumbling]
[rain pouring]

06:38.125 --> 06:39.916
- [Miss Thorna] Come on, girls.
Speed up.

06:42.541 --> 06:44.750
- [Princess] [sneezes] We should
have stayed on the bus.

06:46.125 --> 06:48.291
I'm gonna, I'm gonna sue
if I catch pneumonia.

06:49.250 --> 06:50.791
- First she hates the bus,
now she wants the bus.

06:50.875 --> 06:53.582
Are you ever happy?
- Not when I'm around you.

06:53.666 --> 06:56.666
- Wait, you guys, I think
there might be a hotel here.

06:56.750 --> 06:57.832
- [Miss Thorna] Oh, thank God.

06:57.916 --> 06:59.125
Come on.

06:59.916 --> 07:01.916
[portentous whistling music]

07:02.416 --> 07:05.166
[thunder rumbles]

07:08.791 --> 07:10.958
Does anyone have any service?

07:11.041 --> 07:12.000
- I have two bars.

07:13.666 --> 07:15.125
- I just think we might be in a
dead zone.

07:16.041 --> 07:18.750
[thunder rumbles]

07:19.750 --> 07:20.707
- [Miss Thorna] Oh, hi.

07:20.791 --> 07:22.041
Hi. Hello, hi.

07:22.125 --> 07:23.291
Could we use your phone?

07:23.375 --> 07:25.082
Our bus has broken down
and we're stranded-

07:25.166 --> 07:26.250
We're trying to...
- Yuri.

07:27.416 --> 07:29.041
Let them pass

07:31.791 --> 07:35.291
I beg pardon. My brother
is mute, he gets confused.

07:35.750 --> 07:37.291
- I get it, my sister's deaf

07:37.375 --> 07:39.957
so I have to interpret
everything.

07:40.041 --> 07:41.457
Fucking bullshit

07:41.541 --> 07:44.457
- My name is Osip. How
can I be of service?

07:44.541 --> 07:47.457
- We need a cab. Do you
think you can manage?

07:47.541 --> 07:48.666
- But of course.

07:49.666 --> 07:51.250
Such beautiful creatures
should not be out in the cold.

07:53.416 --> 07:54.582
Come, come.

07:54.666 --> 07:56.041
[uneasy music]

07:56.125 --> 07:57.291
What brings you here?

07:57.375 --> 07:58.291
- We're ballerinas.

08:03.000 --> 08:05.250
- No way. This is my kind of
place.

08:05.916 --> 08:08.916
[bright piano music
reverberates]

08:10.291 --> 08:12.333
- [Princess] This is too weird.

08:12.416 --> 08:13.916
- [Grace] Miss Thorna.
- Huh?

08:14.416 --> 08:15.833
Miss Thorna, this is against my
decency.

08:15.916 --> 08:17.957
There's people gambling. I can't
be here. I can't be here.

08:18.041 --> 08:19.957
- Oh, cover your eyes.
I'm getting a drink.

08:20.041 --> 08:21.291
[Grace gasps]

08:22.041 --> 08:24.041
[patrons clapping]

08:26.166 --> 08:29.791
[singer croons in Hungarian]

08:39.040 --> 08:40.000
Take a picture of me

08:40.750 --> 08:42.000
Zoe stop acting like a child

08:42.415 --> 08:44.625
...but this place is awesome

08:51.290 --> 08:55.165
- [Osip] Ah, that's uh,
that's actually my boss.

08:55.790 --> 08:57.540
She was really something back in
the day.

08:58.665 --> 09:00.375
They said she was the next
Fonteyn,

09:01.541 --> 09:02.916
but there was an accident.

09:03.916 --> 09:07.083
She never danced again.
[woman exhales smoke]

09:07.166 --> 09:09.125
- What is this place?
Like a Nutcracker bar?

09:10.041 --> 09:11.916
- This is my boss's pride and
joy.

09:12.416 --> 09:13.666
- We don't want to be rude,

09:13.750 --> 09:14.833
but we're actually pressed for
time.

09:14.916 --> 09:16.541
- I know.
- We need to get to Budapest.

09:16.916 --> 09:18.708
My girls are dancing there
tomorrow.

09:18.791 --> 09:21.083
What the hell!
- [Miss Thorna] Oh...

09:21.166 --> 09:22.666
They're wet!

09:22.750 --> 09:26.083
- Um, this is uh, this is Sona.

09:26.166 --> 09:27.291
She is the most kind.

09:28.666 --> 09:31.166
She says that you can use
the dryer while you wait.

09:31.875 --> 09:32.833
- [Miss Thorna] Oh, that's
very kind but we don't...

09:32.915 --> 09:35.415
- No, no, no, we insist. We
insist.

09:36.000 --> 09:38.415
Ballerinas deserve the
very best at Teremok Inn.

09:39.040 --> 09:40.415
- Do you have dry clothes?

09:41.415 --> 09:43.915
[piano plays bright classical
music]

09:44.625 --> 09:45.665
- [Osip] In tutus, you look like

09:45.750 --> 09:47.415
a flock of little white birds.

09:49.040 --> 09:50.415
This is so humiliating.

09:50.790 --> 09:51.665
- Eat one.

09:52.290 --> 09:53.833
- Oh, thanks. I'm starved.

09:53.915 --> 09:55.915
- Careful, don't get food on
your clothes.

09:57.000 --> 09:59.165
- Not a problem because I
will not be eating here.

10:04.416 --> 10:05.750
- [Princess] You know that
food is filled with Ebola.

10:05.833 --> 10:07.208
- Meat soup, ew.
- It's fine.

10:07.291 --> 10:08.458
- E coli.

10:08.541 --> 10:09.583
It would be full of E coli.

10:09.666 --> 10:11.833
- Whatever. You've just like
never traveled.

10:11.916 --> 10:13.458
- Girls, please.

10:13.541 --> 10:17.083
- They do not get along. I
mean, how do you dance together?

10:17.166 --> 10:18.708
- God teaches us about love by
giving us

10:18.791 --> 10:20.708
difficult people to work with.

10:20.791 --> 10:22.916
Ballerinas at Teremok...

10:24.125 --> 10:27.666
Yes, yes. There you are.

10:27.750 --> 10:29.333
- [All] Hello.

10:29.416 --> 10:31.416
- Allow me to introduce myself.

10:31.500 --> 10:34.165
My name is Devora Kasimer.
Owner of Teremok Inn.

10:34.500 --> 10:38.583
Osip mentioned that
you have big show, yeah?

10:38.665 --> 10:39.915
- Yeah, we're performing
at

10:40.000 --> 10:42.665
the International Ballet Gala in
Budapest.

10:42.750 --> 10:46.415
And, not to brag, but
it's kind of a big deal.

10:46.500 --> 10:48.708
Only the world's best dancers
get invited.

10:48.790 --> 10:52.458
- I know. I used to be a dancer.

10:52.540 --> 10:54.040
You want me to call you a
minivan to take you to the city?

10:54.125 --> 10:55.083
She owns this... She is a dancer

10:55.165 --> 10:56.958
- Yes, yes. Thank you. Thank you
so much.

10:57.040 --> 10:58.708
- My pleasure.

10:58.790 --> 11:02.291
Sona. [speaks Hungarian]

11:03.791 --> 11:06.500
[ominous music]

11:15.000 --> 11:17.916
- Pasha! Please pass on
my respect to your father.

11:18.000 --> 11:20.166
- Yeah, sure thing, Grand-pop.

11:24.291 --> 11:26.000
Zolly, what up?

11:30.916 --> 11:32.665
- Make sure it gets
to your father.

11:35.625 --> 11:37.750
We appreciate discretion, Pasha.

11:38.415 --> 11:42.415
[hearing aid signal crackling]

11:42.500 --> 11:44.915
[muffled indistinct voices]

11:49.915 --> 11:50.875
What's wrong?

11:52.125 --> 11:53.290
Static...

11:53.375 --> 11:54.625
...I think it got wet

11:56.540 --> 11:57.665
I gotta pee

11:59.290 --> 12:00.916
- My sister has to use the
bathroom.

12:02.750 --> 12:04.250
- Just come with me, sweetheart.

12:05.416 --> 12:07.666
[ear pressure rumbling]

12:08.666 --> 12:10.666
- Ah, well, there's no
need for that, thank you.

12:10.750 --> 12:12.083
I'll, I'll take her.

12:12.166 --> 12:13.166
Thank you.

12:14.291 --> 12:16.791
- Bathroom is up those stairs.

12:21.166 --> 12:23.916
[ominous music]

12:29.625 --> 12:31.791
- Um.... Right, this way.

12:44.375 --> 12:47.750
[velvet scuffs smoothly]

12:57.415 --> 13:01.375
[piano plays "Dance of the Sugar
Plum Fairy"]

13:08.541 --> 13:09.500
- Guys.

13:12.916 --> 13:14.416
I think he wants us to dance.

13:15.916 --> 13:17.333
He's, he's playing Sugar Plum.

13:17.416 --> 13:19.291
Like, we could practice our
variation.

13:20.791 --> 13:22.666
- I could use some practice.

13:22.750 --> 13:24.708
- Okay, let's go. We're going.

13:24.791 --> 13:26.041
Come on. Come on.

13:30.041 --> 13:33.415
[Zoe and Grace giggling]

13:44.625 --> 13:48.665
[piano continues playing
faintly]

13:49.415 --> 13:50.540
[muffled shout]

13:52.500 --> 13:56.125
[encouraging whoops]
- Bravo.

13:58.790 --> 14:00.250
- Come on, Bones.

14:02.250 --> 14:06.916
[muffled ear pressure]

14:08.125 --> 14:12.125
[hearing aid whines and
crackles]

14:15.625 --> 14:20.000
[distant muffled groans]

14:25.916 --> 14:29.500
[pained groans grow louder]

14:32.750 --> 14:34.290
[pained grunt]

14:36.290 --> 14:38.790
- Don't get blood on my desk.
- [Saber] Sorry, Mama.

14:39.790 --> 14:41.790
- Myshinaya Koroleva, please!

14:43.665 --> 14:44.540
You are...

14:44.625 --> 14:46.165
You are a reasonable woman.

14:46.250 --> 14:48.165
[man sobs]

14:48.250 --> 14:49.540
- I am.

14:50.625 --> 14:52.290
Next time I take your tongue.

14:53.415 --> 14:55.790
[man groans]
[Miss Thorna gasps]

14:56.790 --> 15:00.166
[uneasy suspenseful music]

15:00.250 --> 15:02.916
[man screaming]

15:10.166 --> 15:12.791
[intense music]

15:25.000 --> 15:27.208
[piano plays "Dance of
the Sugar Plum Fairy"]

15:27.291 --> 15:30.375
[patrons chattering]

15:37.790 --> 15:40.250
[chattering grows louder]

15:41.415 --> 15:42.708
- Opa!

15:42.790 --> 15:46.833
[people exclaiming and laughing]

15:46.915 --> 15:48.333
[dancers gasping]

15:48.415 --> 15:49.665
- If you want the solo,
you can have the solo.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.665
- Okay.

15:51.665 --> 15:52.790
- [Zoe] Watch it, Princess!

15:58.250 --> 16:01.208
- Hey there, little birdie, you
party with us tonight, yeah?

16:01.291 --> 16:02.541
- Oh no, no thank you.
[Miss Thorna gasps]

16:02.625 --> 16:04.291
- Let's be romantic. You're my
type.

16:04.375 --> 16:06.166
- Sir!
- Hey!

16:06.250 --> 16:07.541
- Get off of me!

16:07.625 --> 16:09.750
- You like to play rough, hmm?

16:10.375 --> 16:12.250
Hmm?
Let's play rough.

16:14.541 --> 16:15.958
- Damn, that's how it's done.

16:16.041 --> 16:17.416
- Girls, get your things. We
need to get out of here.

16:17.500 --> 16:18.333
[gun bangs]

16:18.416 --> 16:20.958
[people screaming]

16:21.041 --> 16:23.291
[person sobbing]

16:23.375 --> 16:25.666
- You see what happens when you
disrespect a man like me, hmm?

16:27.750 --> 16:30.083
Do any of you wanna test me?

16:30.166 --> 16:32.208
This is Markovic territory.

16:32.290 --> 16:34.708
You wanna deal with my father,
hmm?

16:34.790 --> 16:37.958
[Bones sobbing]

16:38.040 --> 16:40.958
You maybe have something to say,
huh?

16:41.040 --> 16:43.083
- [Zoe] Sorry, no, please don't
hurt me.

16:43.165 --> 16:44.665
- [Osip] Hey, hey, Pasha.

16:46.000 --> 16:46.958
Just relax.

16:47.040 --> 16:49.165
Hey, have a drink.

16:49.250 --> 16:51.208
[door clank]
[dramatic sting]

16:51.290 --> 16:52.540
Pasha, come on, come on.

16:52.625 --> 16:53.958
Relax.

16:54.040 --> 16:55.750
- [Devora] What is this
nonsense?

16:56.415 --> 16:57.958
- Myshinaya Koroleva.

16:58.040 --> 17:00.750
You killed a woman in my bar.

17:01.875 --> 17:03.208
[dancers sobbing]

17:03.291 --> 17:04.458
Calm down.

17:04.540 --> 17:06.125
Everything will be all right.

17:06.500 --> 17:08.290
- Okay, he shot-he shot her.

17:09.750 --> 17:11.790
[gasping] He shot-he shot
her in the fucking face!

17:13.750 --> 17:14.708
Call the police.

17:14.790 --> 17:15.790
- Yeah, go and try it.

17:15.875 --> 17:17.625
Call the police!
- Hey!

17:20.165 --> 17:23.290
- Bones, Bones, [clapping]
Bones!

17:27.125 --> 17:30.666
Please, call police. Police,
please!

17:30.750 --> 17:32.833
- Ladies, ladies!
[Grace sobbing]

17:32.916 --> 17:34.541
I will call the police.

17:35.291 --> 17:39.916
Osip, show them the safe room,
hmm?

17:40.000 --> 17:42.541
Basement. Now

17:45.541 --> 17:47.041
Everything will be okay.

17:50.000 --> 17:51.666
I promise.

17:52.250 --> 17:55.041
[Bones cries out]
[dramatic music]

17:56.666 --> 17:59.958
[Bones gasping]

18:00.041 --> 18:00.958
- [Saber] Hey!

18:01.041 --> 18:02.500
Come here!

18:03.250 --> 18:05.958
[Bones gasping]

18:06.041 --> 18:07.958
[exciting dramatic music]

18:08.041 --> 18:09.666
[music stops]

18:11.791 --> 18:13.041
[dramatic music resumes]

18:14.416 --> 18:17.875
[intense music]

18:25.416 --> 18:26.958
- Enough madness.

18:27.041 --> 18:29.333
Follow Osip. He'll take care of
you.

18:29.416 --> 18:30.708
[Grace cries]

18:30.791 --> 18:31.791
I'll separate them.

18:32.291 --> 18:33.208
And keep them quiet.

18:33.291 --> 18:34.833
- Come on.

18:34.916 --> 18:35.791
Follow me.

18:37.041 --> 18:39.000
Everything will be all right.

18:41.041 --> 18:42.041
This way.

18:44.416 --> 18:47.541
[contemplative music]
[girls sobbing]

19:08.666 --> 19:09.541
- Hey, shortie.

19:10.083 --> 19:11.125
Are you lost?

19:11.208 --> 19:13.458
I'm deaf.

19:13.541 --> 19:16.416
What? Wait, you don't hear?

19:23.750 --> 19:24.750
You like tattoos?

19:27.916 --> 19:31.291
You are pretty, like...

19:35.041 --> 19:37.416
[Chloe whispers] You are cute.

19:39.666 --> 19:41.000
- Okay.

19:42.166 --> 19:43.958
- [Osip] The gun just
went off by itself.

19:44.041 --> 19:46.541
- [Princess] No, no, do
not gaslight me, okay?

19:46.625 --> 19:48.083
He shot Miss Thorna right in
front of us-

19:48.166 --> 19:49.916
Like, you are calling the
cops, right?

19:50.000 --> 19:51.333
- My boss is calling them
right now, right now.

19:51.416 --> 19:53.250
- Okay.
- She handles everything, okay?

19:53.875 --> 19:54.958
This is a tragedy, yes?

19:55.041 --> 19:56.583
[Grace gasping for breath]

19:56.666 --> 19:58.916
- Lord, Lord, I can't breathe!

19:59.541 --> 20:00.958
I can't breathe, I can't
breathe!

20:01.041 --> 20:02.291
- Okay, like do something.

20:02.375 --> 20:03.708
[Grace wheezing]

20:03.791 --> 20:06.416
- Hey, you eat this,

20:07.541 --> 20:10.291
you'll feel good in
no time. Okay?

20:10.375 --> 20:11.666
[worried music]

20:13.291 --> 20:15.541
[Grace whimpering]

20:15.625 --> 20:18.291
[ominous music]

20:25.625 --> 20:27.541
- [Devora] What a mess
you've made of my bar.

20:28.666 --> 20:31.500
Get that Brit off my
floor, and move quickly.

20:34.916 --> 20:36.000
- Yeah, do as she says.

20:37.916 --> 20:40.333
- We should have a little chat.

20:40.416 --> 20:42.625
[body sliding]

20:43.541 --> 20:45.458
- Can we get more blood on the
floor?

20:45.541 --> 20:48.000
Sona, grab the mop.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.041
Come.

20:56.250 --> 20:57.916
[banging on door]

21:00.916 --> 21:02.500
[banging on the door]

21:03.041 --> 21:04.583
[latch clanks]

21:04.666 --> 21:06.416
[door creaks]

21:08.041 --> 21:09.500
- Caught me a ballerina.

21:10.291 --> 21:11.666
Hmm.

21:12.000 --> 21:13.458
[Pasha exhaling]

21:13.541 --> 21:14.541
- What's the big deal?

21:15.916 --> 21:18.583
You say this crazy drunk
lady got in my face

21:18.666 --> 21:20.416
when my gun went off.

21:20.500 --> 21:23.708
Whoops, it's not my fault.

21:23.791 --> 21:25.833
- The ballerinas will claim
otherwise.

21:25.916 --> 21:28.916
- Well, if they won't
cooperate, then do what you do.

21:29.625 --> 21:32.291
Take their tongues or slit their
throat.

21:34.541 --> 21:35.916
We can be done with this.

21:36.000 --> 21:38.625
- Sit down. You're making me
dizzy with all your pacing.

21:39.541 --> 21:41.958
We cannot be impulsive.

21:42.041 --> 21:45.416
The disappearance of six
Americans will not go unnoticed.

21:45.500 --> 21:48.083
We must make sure to
have all the information

21:48.166 --> 21:49.916
and be strategic.

21:50.000 --> 21:52.541
But don't worry,
I will take care of you.

21:52.625 --> 21:55.291
[scoffing and laughing]

21:56.041 --> 21:58.000
- You take care of me?

21:59.416 --> 22:00.541
Am I hearing this right?

22:01.791 --> 22:02.666
- Yes.

22:03.791 --> 22:05.541
But it'll come with a price.

22:07.500 --> 22:08.541
- Watch yourself.

22:10.166 --> 22:12.625
I am the son of Lothar the
Butcher.

22:14.750 --> 22:17.708
Devora, there is no chance of
mercy

22:17.791 --> 22:19.166
when you cross my family.

22:23.166 --> 22:24.875
Do not make me summon my father.

22:26.125 --> 22:27.833
- I would like to meet him.

22:27.916 --> 22:31.458
He has declined my invitations
many times.

22:31.541 --> 22:33.541
- My father is a busy man.

22:33.625 --> 22:35.583
He doesn't have time to
drive out to the "boonies",

22:35.666 --> 22:39.375
but one call, and he will make
the trip to make you hurt.

22:46.791 --> 22:47.666
- Hmm.

22:49.291 --> 22:52.041
For many years I paid
for father money.

22:52.125 --> 22:55.208
A debt I inherited from
my own dear Papa.

22:55.291 --> 22:56.875
But those payments stop today.

22:58.541 --> 23:01.166
Tell your father if he
wants his money,

23:01.250 --> 23:03.291
he can pay me a visit.

23:05.666 --> 23:08.166
My envelope, please.

23:14.125 --> 23:16.791
[rope creaking]

23:18.916 --> 23:21.416
- [Grace] No, there
was no one on the road.

23:22.666 --> 23:24.208
- [Sona] Does your family or
friends

23:24.291 --> 23:25.958
know where you broke down?

23:26.041 --> 23:27.708
- No. No.

23:27.791 --> 23:28.708
- What about the theater?

23:28.791 --> 23:30.166
- No.

23:30.250 --> 23:31.333
- Hey, Grace.

23:31.416 --> 23:32.291
[Grace shrieks]

23:32.375 --> 23:33.583
- Bonesy-Jonesy.

23:33.666 --> 23:35.166
You're back.

23:35.250 --> 23:37.666
Bonnie, this is...

23:39.916 --> 23:41.208
Who are you?

23:41.291 --> 23:43.708
- I am not important.
Tell me-

23:43.791 --> 23:45.791
- Grace, don't tell this bitch
anything.

23:46.416 --> 23:48.666
- That girl is very rude.

23:48.750 --> 23:50.208
- She just hates me

23:50.291 --> 23:52.916
because I keep telling
her she might go to hell.

23:53.000 --> 23:53.916
- [Sona] Forget her.

23:54.500 --> 23:56.458
You and I can be best friends.

23:56.541 --> 23:57.958
- Fun!

23:58.041 --> 23:59.708
We could eat pineapple pizza!

23:59.791 --> 24:01.041
- What did you people do to
Grace?

24:01.125 --> 24:02.333
- Quiet!

24:02.416 --> 24:03.791
Grace.
- Hmm?

24:04.666 --> 24:06.166
- Be my friend.
- Mmm.

24:06.250 --> 24:09.583
- Tell me who knows you come to
Teremok Inn.

24:09.666 --> 24:10.875
- Everybody knows.

24:11.666 --> 24:14.916
My dad, her parents, the
entire ballet company knows.

24:15.000 --> 24:17.041
Okay? They're gonna come looking
for us.

24:17.125 --> 24:20.625
- Bonnie, how can I save
your soul if you lie?

24:24.916 --> 24:26.083
No one's coming.

24:26.166 --> 24:27.416
- Grace, you fucking idiot.

24:29.875 --> 24:31.041
Let me see Devora.

24:32.875 --> 24:34.458
Help us.

24:34.541 --> 24:35.666
Please.

24:36.416 --> 24:39.166
- [Sona] I would, but disobey
Devora,

24:40.416 --> 24:41.791
she take your tongue.

24:43.666 --> 24:48.583
[menacing music]
[footsteps fading]

24:48.666 --> 24:50.416
[door clanking]

24:53.500 --> 24:56.000
[eerie music]

25:05.750 --> 25:09.416
[rotary phone dial clicking]

25:22.291 --> 25:25.000
- Doktor, I have a vermin
problem.

25:32.541 --> 25:33.958
[patrons chattering]

25:34.041 --> 25:34.916
- Pasha.

25:37.541 --> 25:39.250
What did Devora want?

25:40.291 --> 25:41.250
- Nothing.

25:44.166 --> 25:45.791
Let's get out of this rat hole.

25:46.416 --> 25:49.041
- Pasha, give me the envelope.

25:49.791 --> 25:50.750
The money.

25:52.166 --> 25:53.416
- I gave it back to Devora.

25:54.291 --> 25:55.333
- What?

25:55.416 --> 25:57.583
We can't return empty-handed.

25:57.666 --> 25:58.958
Your father is going to kill us,
Pasha.

25:59.041 --> 26:00.041
- Shut the fuck up.

26:00.541 --> 26:03.208
- [Sona] Jesus girl, she spill
everything.

26:03.291 --> 26:04.916
But the runaway could be
trouble.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.291
She is not like the others.

26:07.166 --> 26:08.833
- [Devora] The only problem
these dancers are for me

26:08.916 --> 26:10.458
is if anyone knows they're here.

26:10.541 --> 26:12.833
- No one knows, Myshinaya
Koroleva.

26:12.916 --> 26:14.750
- Good, then Doktor can do his
job.

26:15.541 --> 26:17.875
Osip, gather the dancers'
stuff and have Yuri burn it.

26:27.541 --> 26:28.791
[Artyom sighs]

26:29.291 --> 26:30.416
- Hello, Mama.

26:30.500 --> 26:33.875
What are you doing you little
rascal?

26:34.291 --> 26:35.416
- No need for Hungarian.

26:36.291 --> 26:37.916
Bitch doesn't hear or speak.

26:40.791 --> 26:42.333
- Come.

26:42.416 --> 26:43.541
Come with me, sweetheart.

26:45.416 --> 26:47.291
These boys...
[Sona hisses]

26:49.041 --> 26:51.291
[Osip chuckling]

26:57.125 --> 27:00.041
[brain squelching]

27:05.791 --> 27:08.666
How is my big boy so sensitive?

27:09.541 --> 27:10.666
- Sorry, Mama.

27:11.041 --> 27:12.791
- It's not your fault.

27:12.875 --> 27:14.916
I was too gentle with you.

27:15.791 --> 27:16.791
[brain squelches]

27:18.541 --> 27:19.416
Bingo.

27:25.041 --> 27:27.875
[dramatic music]

27:31.791 --> 27:34.666
[music crescendos]

27:48.916 --> 27:52.791
[Bones gasping]

27:52.875 --> 27:54.291
[shoulder popping]

28:02.791 --> 28:04.416
- You stupid piece of shit.

28:04.500 --> 28:06.291
- Why are you mad at me?

28:06.375 --> 28:07.833
I love you.

28:07.916 --> 28:09.375
- What's wrong with you?

28:09.791 --> 28:12.291
- Osip gave me pocket chocolate.

28:12.375 --> 28:15.708
I feel really weird, but
I also feel warm inside.

28:15.791 --> 28:16.708
- You're high.

28:16.791 --> 28:17.916
- High?

28:18.000 --> 28:19.958
I can't be high! I can't be
high!

28:20.041 --> 28:21.416
I can't be high!

28:21.916 --> 28:23.083
What about the showcase?

28:23.166 --> 28:24.666
I feel sick!

28:24.750 --> 28:26.041
- Good, get whatever they
gave you outta your system.

28:26.125 --> 28:27.541
Come on!
- I can't! I need help!

28:27.625 --> 28:28.833
I can't, Bonnie.

28:28.916 --> 28:29.958
Help.

28:30.041 --> 28:31.791
- What kinda ballerina doesn't
know

28:31.875 --> 28:33.166
how to make themselves throw up?

28:33.541 --> 28:37.291
[Grace retching and coughing]

28:39.500 --> 28:41.083
- Goulash.

28:41.166 --> 28:42.041
[Bones scoffing]

28:42.125 --> 28:45.958
[gate clanking]
[key jangling]

28:46.041 --> 28:48.125
- [Sona] Osip, bring up some
palinka.

28:48.666 --> 28:51.791
- No problem.
Be there in a minute.

28:52.125 --> 28:54.916
[gates creak and clank]

28:59.875 --> 29:01.666
[Osip inhales]

29:01.750 --> 29:04.416
[ominous music]

29:15.041 --> 29:17.416
[latch clicking]

29:21.916 --> 29:23.291
- Shit!

29:23.375 --> 29:24.916
He's coming.
Pretend to be asleep.

29:25.000 --> 29:27.916
[Grace whimpering]

29:32.541 --> 29:34.583
[eerie music]

29:34.666 --> 29:37.375
[door clanking]

29:39.541 --> 29:40.791
- [Osip] Grace.

29:42.666 --> 29:44.791
[door crashes shut]

29:46.750 --> 29:49.291
[key turns in lock]

29:50.166 --> 29:51.041
Grace.

29:56.916 --> 29:58.541
You ready for more fun?

29:58.625 --> 30:00.291
[Osip slips on vomit]

30:00.916 --> 30:04.166
Oh, you're, you're sick.

30:04.250 --> 30:07.666
Hey, hey, it's all right.

30:08.916 --> 30:09.916
It's okay.

30:10.875 --> 30:14.666
You know, you look like a little
swan.

30:16.916 --> 30:21.625
I never, I never told nobody
about it, but [inhaling]

30:25.041 --> 30:27.541
I kinda got a thing for birds.

30:30.625 --> 30:33.666
I think it's, it's the necks
that I like.

30:35.291 --> 30:36.916
So soft.

30:38.875 --> 30:41.333
[Grace gasping]

30:41.416 --> 30:43.291
- The Lord rebuke you, Satan!

30:43.375 --> 30:44.791
Satan!

30:44.875 --> 30:47.458
- [voice distorted] Oh
shit, you have bad trip.

30:47.541 --> 30:48.416
It's okay.

30:49.916 --> 30:51.166
[Grace whimpering]

30:51.250 --> 30:53.291
[nutcrackers creaking]

30:53.375 --> 30:54.458
- Run!

30:54.541 --> 30:55.458
- Run!

30:55.541 --> 30:56.458
[distorted voices echo]

30:56.541 --> 30:58.083
- Jesus, Jesus, I want out!

30:58.166 --> 30:59.041
I want out!

30:59.125 --> 31:01.041
- You can pray all you want.

31:02.000 --> 31:05.000
You're not going anywhere,
ballerina.

31:05.875 --> 31:06.791
- Hey!

31:07.291 --> 31:10.666
[both screaming]

31:10.750 --> 31:13.250
[Grace screaming]

31:15.750 --> 31:17.125
[both grunting]

31:18.541 --> 31:20.333
[Grace screaming]

31:20.416 --> 31:21.833
[Osip screaming]

31:21.916 --> 31:23.666
[dramatic music]

31:23.750 --> 31:27.416
[all grunting and screaming]

31:32.166 --> 31:35.375
[Bones screaming]

31:36.375 --> 31:40.041
[Princess and Zoe screaming]

31:49.750 --> 31:51.625
[both screaming]

31:55.791 --> 31:58.625
[Bones screaming]

32:06.416 --> 32:07.958
[Princess exclaiming]

32:08.041 --> 32:10.750
[dancers crying]

32:23.541 --> 32:25.791
- Your dancing days are over,
ballerina.

32:25.875 --> 32:27.833
- No, no!

32:27.916 --> 32:30.791
[sinister music]

32:30.875 --> 32:33.291
[arm clanks]

32:35.916 --> 32:37.291
[Grace screaming]

32:49.416 --> 32:52.791
[Princess and Zoe scream]

32:55.666 --> 32:59.791
[Artyom sings in Hungarian]
[patrons clapping]

33:09.750 --> 33:13.291
[Artyom continues singing in
Hungarian]

33:13.375 --> 33:16.916
[patrons continue clapping]

33:19.166 --> 33:21.125
- Give me a tray of shots, will
you?

33:21.666 --> 33:23.041
- Oh, are we celebrating?

33:23.125 --> 33:25.416
- No. It's tragic.

33:26.791 --> 33:28.541
Between the five ballerinas,

33:28.625 --> 33:31.458
there is almost 100 years of
training,

33:31.541 --> 33:34.541
dedication, pain, passion, and
discipline,

33:35.166 --> 33:39.125
all to be extinguished by
the folly of one idiot.

33:43.125 --> 33:46.291
So no, I'm not celebrating.

33:46.791 --> 33:48.166
I'm grieving.

33:50.291 --> 33:52.541
May their sacrifices not be in
vain.

33:54.000 --> 33:55.166
- Here you are.

33:56.750 --> 34:01.500
[Devora and patrons
applauding and cheering]

34:06.166 --> 34:07.666
- Excellent. Bravo.

34:14.250 --> 34:15.458
Keep it flowing.

34:15.541 --> 34:17.541
I want Pasha and his boys well
oiled.

34:20.041 --> 34:23.541
[intense mysterious music]

34:34.250 --> 34:36.250
Drink up, little mice.

34:40.500 --> 34:41.541
- [Princess] What's wrong with
her?

34:41.625 --> 34:43.250
She's acting weirder than usual.

34:43.666 --> 34:45.041
- [Bones] This fuck drugged her.

34:45.125 --> 34:46.208
- [Zoe] We have to get out of
here.

34:46.291 --> 34:47.416
- No, really?

34:49.250 --> 34:51.916
Why couldn't you have just
waited for the authorities

34:52.000 --> 34:53.541
to come and do their job?

34:53.625 --> 34:55.166
Why did you have to cause
trouble?

34:55.250 --> 34:56.625
- Miss Thorna is dead.

34:57.291 --> 34:59.666
If the cops are coming,
they'd be here by now.

35:00.375 --> 35:01.833
I know this is hard for you to
understand

35:01.916 --> 35:04.208
because all your life help
has been one phone call away,

35:04.291 --> 35:05.416
[Princess scoffs]

35:05.916 --> 35:07.666
but we're on our own.

35:07.750 --> 35:09.708
No one is coming to save us.

35:09.791 --> 35:11.208
- You're wrong.

35:11.291 --> 35:12.333
- We're a bunch of foreigners

35:12.416 --> 35:13.916
on the other side of the world.

35:14.291 --> 35:15.333
The cheapest, most efficient way

35:15.416 --> 35:17.458
to deal with this situation is
to kill us.

35:17.541 --> 35:19.416
- [Zoe] We have to get out of
here.

35:19.500 --> 35:22.125
- Stop saying we have to get out
of here.

35:22.666 --> 35:24.041
We know if we stay, we're gonna
die,

35:24.750 --> 35:25.708
so saying "We have to get out of
here"

35:25.791 --> 35:26.916
over and over again does
nothing.

35:27.875 --> 35:30.250
We need to stop talking
and start doing because,

35:32.416 --> 35:33.666
we have to get out of here.

35:34.250 --> 35:39.291
[tense music]

35:57.250 --> 35:59.416
- Don't fret. I'll be back soon.

36:02.250 --> 36:03.958
- You want the cobra?
- Mmm-hmm.

36:04.041 --> 36:05.083
- What, do you want the cobra?

36:05.166 --> 36:06.083
- Yes!
- Give it!

36:06.166 --> 36:07.166
- I got you!

36:07.250 --> 36:08.250
Take the cobra.

36:10.041 --> 36:11.166
Yeah, Pasha.

36:11.250 --> 36:12.458
[all laughing]

36:12.541 --> 36:13.500
- Evening, comrades.

36:20.041 --> 36:23.916
Pasha, perhaps one day
you'll be housebroken.

36:31.166 --> 36:34.125
- Artyom, what is that cretin
doing here?

36:34.666 --> 36:37.375
- Devora.
- [giggles] Doktor.

36:37.875 --> 36:39.541
- Mon amour.

36:41.541 --> 36:42.708
You removed the bullet?

36:42.791 --> 36:45.125
- Of course.
- Nice.

36:46.291 --> 36:49.583
I take teeth, eyes, fingertips,

36:49.666 --> 36:51.833
then do the same for ballerinas.

36:51.916 --> 36:54.375
No one will be able to identify
them.

36:55.250 --> 36:57.000
[knuckles crack]
Lovely.

36:58.041 --> 36:59.666
She's never going to give me
that tape.

37:00.750 --> 37:02.291
Now she's bringing in this
cretin Doktor

37:02.375 --> 37:04.083
so she can say to my Papa,

37:04.166 --> 37:05.916
"I handled it, not Pasha."

37:10.041 --> 37:11.666
I want you to kill the
ballerinas.

37:11.750 --> 37:14.583
[tense music]

37:14.666 --> 37:16.416
- Your father will be proud.

37:16.750 --> 37:17.791
- I know.

37:18.541 --> 37:20.791
[door creaks]

37:21.875 --> 37:24.166
[tense music]

37:29.000 --> 37:29.916
- Come on!

37:33.541 --> 37:34.875
This way.

37:42.791 --> 37:44.416
[whispers] Stay. Stay.

37:45.541 --> 37:48.041
[tense music]

37:51.666 --> 37:53.000
Come on, we can
sneak out this way.

37:57.166 --> 37:59.333
- The devil will throw you into
prison.

37:59.416 --> 38:01.666
You will be tested, but do not
be afraid.

38:03.000 --> 38:06.958
Revelation, chapter two:
verse ten.

38:07.041 --> 38:07.958
- Shh!
[Grace gasps]

38:08.041 --> 38:09.291
Keep your verse down!

38:12.875 --> 38:13.791
- Fuck!

38:15.250 --> 38:17.958
Guys, we might be able
to go through the walls.

38:18.041 --> 38:19.458
[wall sloshes]

38:19.541 --> 38:21.333
[ballerinas lightly gasp]

38:21.416 --> 38:23.041
[lock clinks]
[men laughing]

38:23.125 --> 38:24.916
- Get back. Go, go, go!

38:25.000 --> 38:27.500
[tense music]

38:28.166 --> 38:32.625
- [chuckles] The cobra is coming
for you.

38:34.750 --> 38:40.000
[tense music continues]

38:41.750 --> 38:44.791
[Fadey pants]

38:44.875 --> 38:46.958
Hey, you too drunk?

38:47.041 --> 38:50.333
- [snorts] No such thing.

38:50.416 --> 38:53.875
[tense music continues]

38:55.916 --> 38:57.500
- Find them.
- Okay.

39:03.916 --> 39:07.208
[tense music fades]

39:07.291 --> 39:09.458
[door thuds]
- [gasps] Shh!

39:09.541 --> 39:12.916
[serious string music]

39:14.041 --> 39:15.041
There's two of them.

39:16.916 --> 39:18.916
- I don't wanna die.

39:19.000 --> 39:21.083
- I think we can take them.

39:21.166 --> 39:23.166
- "Take them." Are you nuts?

39:24.791 --> 39:27.791
- No, seriously. I am not
strong enough.

39:29.291 --> 39:32.208
- Bullshit. I've seen you dance.

39:32.291 --> 39:33.458
People assume we're these
delicate,

39:33.541 --> 39:35.416
fragile little things, but we're
not.

39:35.500 --> 39:38.083
We perform sick, hurt,
and on bleeding feet

39:38.166 --> 39:39.291
all while keeping a smile on our
face,

39:39.375 --> 39:42.166
so don't tell me you're not
strong, okay?

39:44.166 --> 39:46.875
[ominous music]

39:51.291 --> 39:52.666
- You guys, you guys!

39:54.541 --> 39:56.166
Our ballet bags.

40:00.250 --> 40:03.250
[zipper echo rings]

40:04.916 --> 40:08.375
[ominous music continues]

40:12.250 --> 40:14.666
- Vlad? Vlad.

40:15.916 --> 40:17.416
Osip is dead.

40:18.041 --> 40:19.166
This is bad for Pasha.

40:19.250 --> 40:21.041
[Vlad exhales]

40:21.125 --> 40:22.041
- They are here.

40:22.916 --> 40:24.416
Yeah.

40:24.500 --> 40:27.333
[ballerinas lightly gasp]

40:27.416 --> 40:30.083
- [Fadey] Girls, we know you're
in there!

40:30.166 --> 40:31.666
Get out!
- He's got a gun.

40:31.750 --> 40:33.416
- This is your last
chance!

40:33.791 --> 40:35.041
- Fuck off!

40:35.500 --> 40:38.250
[dramatic music]

40:40.250 --> 40:42.166
[dramatic music crescendos]

40:42.250 --> 40:43.583
[ballerinas grunt]
[door thudding]

40:43.666 --> 40:47.458
[bones crack]
[Fadey yelps and grunts]

40:47.541 --> 40:49.958
[scissors ring]
[ballerinas grunt]

40:50.041 --> 40:52.416
[scissors pierce]
[Fadey yells]

40:52.500 --> 40:53.958
[door slams]
[ballerinas shrieking]

40:54.041 --> 40:55.291
[Fadey crying]

40:55.375 --> 40:56.458
[Vlad yells]

40:56.541 --> 41:00.416
[door booming]
[ballerinas gasping]

41:00.500 --> 41:02.708
[Vlad yells]
[door thuds and opens]

41:02.791 --> 41:04.333
[ballerinas grunt and scream]

41:04.416 --> 41:05.916
[scissors pierce]
[Vlad yells]

41:06.000 --> 41:08.625
[ballerinas and Vlad grunting]

41:10.041 --> 41:11.166
[ballerina growls]

41:12.166 --> 41:13.541
[Vlad yells]

41:13.625 --> 41:15.541
[ballerina shrieks]
[Vlad grunting]

41:15.625 --> 41:17.208
[ballerina cries]

41:17.291 --> 41:19.958
[scissors pierce]
[Vlad groans]

41:20.041 --> 41:23.000
[everyone groaning]

41:23.500 --> 41:24.916
[Fadey mumbling]

41:26.791 --> 41:28.500
[skin tears]
- Ow! Fuck!

41:30.291 --> 41:31.333
[Princess and Fadey grunt]

41:31.416 --> 41:34.291
[Princess yelps]

41:34.375 --> 41:36.791
[Vlad grunting]

41:36.875 --> 41:38.666
[Vlad groans]

41:38.750 --> 41:40.083
[ballerina shrieks]

41:40.166 --> 41:42.958
[ballerinas groan and gasp]

41:43.041 --> 41:44.708
[fingers crack]
[Princess yelping]

41:44.791 --> 41:47.041
- [Princess] Zoe! Zoe, help me!

41:47.125 --> 41:49.833
Shoot him! Shoot him, Zoe!

41:49.916 --> 41:51.291
[ballerinas shriek]

41:51.375 --> 41:52.791
[bullets clanging]
[Fadey gasps]

41:52.875 --> 41:54.291
[Fadey screams]

41:54.791 --> 41:56.041
- Okay, the gun ran out!

41:56.125 --> 41:56.958
The gun ran out!

41:57.041 --> 41:58.541
[Fadey yells in foreign
language]

41:58.625 --> 42:00.083
- I'm sorry!
- Don't apologize to him.

42:00.166 --> 42:01.333
- We're fucked. We are so
fucked!

42:01.416 --> 42:02.916
- Give me a blade.

42:05.166 --> 42:07.666
[tense music]

42:08.666 --> 42:10.458
- Your go.
- Kill them.

42:10.541 --> 42:11.916
[Fadey and Vlad grunt]
- No, no.

42:12.000 --> 42:12.875
Okay.

42:15.166 --> 42:16.166
- Come on.

42:16.250 --> 42:18.416
These guys are drunk and out of
shape

42:18.500 --> 42:20.666
and we're prima fucking
ballerinas.

42:20.750 --> 42:22.458
[tense music crescendos]

42:22.541 --> 42:23.583
[Fadey yells]

42:23.666 --> 42:24.958
[Fadey yelps]

42:25.041 --> 42:27.083
[Vlad grunting]

42:27.166 --> 42:30.166
[Vlad yelping]

42:30.250 --> 42:35.041
[Fadey grunting]
[ballerinas shriek and grunt]

42:35.125 --> 42:37.291
[tense music continues]

42:37.375 --> 42:38.583
[Princess yells]

42:38.666 --> 42:39.791
[Fadey yelps]

42:39.875 --> 42:41.083
- Oh!

42:41.166 --> 42:42.541
[Bones grunts]

42:42.625 --> 42:45.708
[Vlad yelping and grunting]

42:45.791 --> 42:48.416
[Bones yelps]

42:48.500 --> 42:50.791
[dramatic music]
[Vlad yelps]

42:52.375 --> 42:54.208
[Bones groaning]

42:54.291 --> 42:56.666
[hopeful music]
[Princess panting]

42:58.041 --> 42:59.458
- No! [shrieks]

42:59.541 --> 43:01.208
[Princess thuds and yelps]

43:01.291 --> 43:02.458
No! No!

43:02.541 --> 43:04.083
No! Ah!

43:04.166 --> 43:06.000
[Vlad yelps]

43:06.083 --> 43:06.958
[Vlad grunts]

43:07.041 --> 43:09.583
No, you don't!

43:09.666 --> 43:10.958
[Vlad thudding]

43:11.041 --> 43:12.583
[Vlad yelps]
[Bones gasps]

43:12.666 --> 43:14.458
[tense music]

43:14.541 --> 43:16.083
[Grace shrieks]

43:16.166 --> 43:18.666
[Fadey grunts]
[Grace thuds and yelps]

43:22.416 --> 43:26.041
[Vlad and Bones grunting]

43:27.916 --> 43:28.833
[Vlad grunts]

43:28.916 --> 43:30.416
[Bones grunts]

43:34.500 --> 43:36.708
[Vlad grunts]
[tense music swells]

43:36.791 --> 43:39.041
[Fadey grunts]
[Zoe shrieking]

43:43.041 --> 43:48.041
[tense music softens]

43:50.000 --> 43:52.458
[Grace screams]
[tense music swells]

43:52.541 --> 43:55.333
[Fadey thuds and yelps]
[Grace continues screaming]

43:55.416 --> 43:56.708
[blade rings]
[Grace violently shrieks]

43:56.791 --> 43:58.791
[Fadey yelps]

43:59.791 --> 44:03.333
[tense music crescendos]

44:03.416 --> 44:05.541
[tense music settles]

44:11.250 --> 44:13.916
[bright music]

44:22.041 --> 44:24.375
- Holy fucking shit. [panting]

44:27.291 --> 44:28.916
That toe blade is sick.

44:29.916 --> 44:30.875
- Happy accident.

44:31.666 --> 44:32.541
- I must have one.

44:44.041 --> 44:45.625
- So there's no going out that
way.

44:45.708 --> 44:46.583
- [Devora] Another round of
drinks.

44:46.666 --> 44:47.875
[patrons cheering]

44:47.958 --> 44:48.833
- Do you hear that?

44:48.916 --> 44:50.083
- What?

44:50.166 --> 44:52.208
- How can she be having a good
time after what happened?

44:52.291 --> 44:53.458
They killed Miss Thorna.

44:53.541 --> 44:54.583
- Okay, Bones, you have to
focus.

44:54.666 --> 44:55.833
We have to find a back door.

44:55.916 --> 44:57.541
- Why would a back door go
upstairs?

44:57.625 --> 44:59.791
- Why would we go upstairs?

44:59.875 --> 45:01.458
God, there's gotta be like a
fire exit or something.

45:01.541 --> 45:03.708
- Because Chloe went up
there to go to the bathroom.

45:03.791 --> 45:05.291
Were you just gonna leave her?

45:09.791 --> 45:12.708
Oh my God, you guys forgot about
Chloe?

45:12.791 --> 45:15.708
- Okay, okay, we'll come back
and get her once we get help.

45:15.791 --> 45:18.166
- No, that might be too late!

45:18.250 --> 45:20.666
She's all alone. Her
hearing aid is broken.

45:21.875 --> 45:24.583
I told my dad I'd look out for
her.

45:24.666 --> 45:26.541
- Boy, you're just doing
like an A+ job, aren't you?

45:26.625 --> 45:27.916
- Shut up, Princess.

45:28.000 --> 45:29.416
Why do you have to be
so selfish all the time?

45:29.500 --> 45:31.083
- I can't leave my sister.

45:31.166 --> 45:32.958
- Nobody is leaving anybody!

45:33.041 --> 45:34.375
- Speak for yourself.

45:35.791 --> 45:37.791
I'm out of here. Grace, let's
go.

45:45.291 --> 45:47.000
Fine! Whatever.

45:47.916 --> 45:48.916
You all suck.

45:51.250 --> 45:52.291
Enjoy getting killed.

45:55.750 --> 45:56.666
- Come on.

45:59.041 --> 46:02.000
[soft eerie music]

46:08.791 --> 46:11.541
- These stairs go up, but
if you're up, they go down.

46:11.625 --> 46:13.458
Hmm.

46:13.541 --> 46:14.666
- That's the first time in my
life

46:14.750 --> 46:16.333
I'm actually jealous of you.

46:16.416 --> 46:18.375
- Thou shall not covet
thy neighbor's buzz.

46:25.500 --> 46:30.291
[eerie music continues]
[ballerinas panting]

46:32.500 --> 46:35.416
- Guys, Chloe could still be in
here.

46:41.541 --> 46:43.333
- What are you doing?

46:43.416 --> 46:45.208
Go back downstairs
before you cause problem.

46:45.291 --> 46:46.375
- Make us.

46:49.041 --> 46:52.333
Be cool. We talk this over,
yeah?

46:52.416 --> 46:54.791
- Where is my sister?

46:54.875 --> 46:58.291
- The deaf one? She's
down the hall chilling.

46:58.375 --> 47:00.458
Now, excuse me.

47:00.541 --> 47:03.541
- I would, but I'm kind
of a vindictive shit.

47:05.000 --> 47:07.666
[serious music]

47:09.541 --> 47:12.166
[Vlad gasping]

47:18.416 --> 47:19.750
- What happened?

47:21.166 --> 47:23.875
[blood sloshes]

47:26.041 --> 47:27.041
- [weakly] Ballerinas.

47:31.750 --> 47:34.541
[serious music continues]

47:34.625 --> 47:38.833
[Princess gasping and panting]

47:38.916 --> 47:42.416
[men distantly chattering]

47:50.791 --> 47:52.958
[lock clicks]

47:53.041 --> 47:57.083
[men continue chattering]

47:57.166 --> 48:00.458
[Princess panting]

48:00.541 --> 48:02.708
[blade rings]

48:02.791 --> 48:07.666
[intense music]
[Doktor humming]

48:09.291 --> 48:14.333
[Princess gasps]
[bones snapping]

48:14.416 --> 48:17.750
[eerie music]
[Doktor continues humming]

48:29.541 --> 48:32.666
[eerie music swells]

48:36.916 --> 48:39.791
- [Saber] Hey.
[eerie music ends]

48:39.875 --> 48:41.208
- Finally!

48:41.291 --> 48:42.833
I have been looking all
over to talk to someone

48:42.916 --> 48:43.916
about the wifi.

48:45.541 --> 48:47.083
- What?
- Like, your service

48:47.166 --> 48:48.916
is seriously inexcusable.

48:49.000 --> 48:51.958
Like, hello, I would've fixed
that like yesterday.

48:52.041 --> 48:53.916
You know, I'm watching this
reality television show.

48:54.000 --> 48:55.833
It's like a dating show, but
I'm watching it ironically,

48:55.916 --> 48:59.916
but secretly, I love it, and
I'm three episodes behind.

49:00.000 --> 49:00.916
- What are you talking about?

49:01.000 --> 49:02.208
- Do you think that you could
find

49:02.291 --> 49:05.083
true love on a dating show?

49:05.166 --> 49:06.583
Because one time, I went to this
dive bar

49:06.666 --> 49:08.583
that rich people go to
for like street cred

49:08.666 --> 49:10.500
and I met this healer and,

49:12.125 --> 49:14.708
well, she told me that I
have a heart condition.

49:14.791 --> 49:16.333
- Oh.
- I know.

49:16.416 --> 49:19.291
She said that I have a block in
my heart

49:20.541 --> 49:22.166
when it comes to love.

49:23.375 --> 49:26.458
So I just don't have
the emotional capacity

49:26.541 --> 49:27.791
to like talk about it right now,

49:27.875 --> 49:29.666
so like I'll just go back
downstairs

49:29.750 --> 49:31.666
and you deal with the wifi.

49:31.750 --> 49:32.625
Okay?

49:36.041 --> 49:36.916
Thank you.

49:51.875 --> 49:54.791
[Princess gasping]

50:03.041 --> 50:04.583
[Princess sobs]

50:04.666 --> 50:07.166
[movie blares]

50:07.250 --> 50:10.166
[popcorn crunches]

50:12.916 --> 50:15.916
[movie continues blaring]

50:16.000 --> 50:19.708
[doors rattle and creak]

50:19.791 --> 50:22.916
[movie continues blaring]
[woman screams in movie]

50:24.125 --> 50:26.125
- [Zoe] Chloe, thank God!

50:27.875 --> 50:28.791
Thank God.

50:32.375 --> 50:35.416
- Holy shit.
- Wow.

50:36.625 --> 50:37.916
- [Bones] She's certifiable.

50:38.791 --> 50:40.166
You're alright?

50:40.250 --> 50:41.791
Yeah why wouldn't I be?

50:42.791 --> 50:45.458
What did you do to your
costumes?

50:45.541 --> 50:46.916
Is that blood?

50:48.375 --> 50:50.000
- Is that a hickey?

50:50.666 --> 50:51.833
Zoe. Shut up!

50:51.916 --> 50:53.000
Stop it!

50:55.666 --> 50:56.875
- [Bones] Bingo.
- Mind your own business.

50:58.000 --> 50:59.000
Put it back.

50:59.625 --> 51:00.541
Chloe.

51:01.541 --> 51:03.000
- We have to go.

51:03.416 --> 51:04.791
Can we wait?

51:04.875 --> 51:08.458
A cute boy said he would give me
a tattoo.

51:08.541 --> 51:11.791
Um, she's waiting for a
boy to give her a tattoo.

51:13.541 --> 51:15.083
What should I do?

51:15.166 --> 51:16.666
- Don't look at us. She's your
sister.

51:18.541 --> 51:21.666
[ballerinas grunting]

51:24.125 --> 51:25.458
- I hear someone. Run!

51:25.541 --> 51:28.541
[suspenseful music]

51:34.250 --> 51:35.166
[gasps]

51:35.250 --> 51:38.250
[footsteps tapping]

51:39.875 --> 51:41.041
- Be quiet.

51:41.125 --> 51:44.875
[suspenseful music continues]

51:56.166 --> 51:58.791
[metal clunks]

52:00.000 --> 52:00.916
- Oh, it's you.

52:03.916 --> 52:04.875
Thought you left.

52:06.041 --> 52:07.333
- Be nice, she's crying.

52:07.416 --> 52:08.958
- No, I'm not.

52:09.041 --> 52:11.708
I have allergies and this
place is full of mold.

52:11.791 --> 52:13.500
- Here, this will sober you up.

52:15.541 --> 52:18.250
[whipped cream hisses]

52:19.791 --> 52:21.458
You didn't get very far going
solo.

52:21.541 --> 52:23.083
- I felt bad for you
losers so I came back.

52:23.166 --> 52:24.916
- Hmm. Yeah, right.

52:25.000 --> 52:26.166
Bet you froze, and you've just
been hiding

52:26.250 --> 52:27.541
in here the whole time.

52:29.416 --> 52:30.333
- Actually, I saw what they were
doing

52:30.416 --> 52:32.333
to Miss Thorna's body.

52:32.416 --> 52:33.583
They're chopping off her
fingertips

52:33.666 --> 52:35.083
and gouging out her eyes.

52:35.166 --> 52:36.541
[whipped cream hisses]
- [Zoe] Oh, my God.

52:38.166 --> 52:39.833
What happened to Miss Thorna?

52:39.916 --> 52:41.583
Miss Thorna's dead.

52:41.666 --> 52:43.291
That's not funny.

52:43.375 --> 52:45.541
Why would you say that?

52:45.625 --> 52:47.625
- Will you listen to me for
once?

52:52.375 --> 52:55.583
[upbeat piano music]

52:55.666 --> 52:56.541
- Gentlemen,

52:58.166 --> 53:02.958
I have provided safe haven
for you and your frivolities.

53:03.041 --> 53:05.208
Now I ask a favor.

53:05.291 --> 53:06.791
There are four
[ominous music]

53:06.875 --> 53:09.958
naughty little girls missing in
the house.

53:10.041 --> 53:13.041
Hunt them, find them,

53:13.125 --> 53:14.458
and silence them.

53:14.541 --> 53:19.958
[footsteps and chattering]

53:20.041 --> 53:21.500
- You're too late.

53:23.291 --> 53:24.666
My boys have taken care of it.

53:26.416 --> 53:29.791
- Your boys are all dead.

53:29.875 --> 53:34.541
Your father is miles away,
and you are all alone now.

53:35.250 --> 53:36.541
Little mouse.

53:38.291 --> 53:39.791
- Hey, I stole that.

53:39.875 --> 53:41.708
- My daddy's country club
has a shooting range.

53:41.791 --> 53:43.333
I know how to use a gun.
- I'm so sorry.

53:43.416 --> 53:44.916
I'll believe it when I see it.

53:48.125 --> 53:50.750
Okay then.
- [Grace] What's this?

53:52.916 --> 53:55.583
[mysterious music]

53:55.666 --> 53:58.208
- Holy shit. You found us a
phone.

53:58.291 --> 54:00.916
- Oh, my God! I'm gonna call the
police.

54:01.000 --> 54:03.250
Move! I'll get us out of here
ASAP.

54:06.041 --> 54:09.458
[sighs] Does anyone know how
to use this caveman bullshit?

54:09.541 --> 54:11.916
- Turn the wheel with your
finger and dial, dumbass.

54:12.000 --> 54:14.250
- Oh, okay. Yeah.

54:17.541 --> 54:18.875
Oh.

54:25.000 --> 54:27.708
This is a very ineffective
way to make a phone call.

54:27.791 --> 54:30.166
It's taking a hundred years.

54:30.250 --> 54:31.333
[line ringing]

54:31.416 --> 54:34.041
- Papa, no. Not drunk much.

54:34.125 --> 54:37.041
[mysterious music]

54:38.750 --> 54:41.666
No, Vlad cannot take me home.
He's dead.

54:44.166 --> 54:46.916
Yes. And Fadey too.

54:50.166 --> 54:51.416
I'm at Teremok.

54:54.041 --> 54:55.541
Yes. I understand.

54:56.750 --> 54:57.791
Thank you, Papa.

54:59.041 --> 55:01.250
Thank you. Thank you.

55:08.916 --> 55:09.791
Devora!

55:12.666 --> 55:14.250
My father is on his way here.

55:15.500 --> 55:16.666
- You lie.

55:17.791 --> 55:19.458
Lothar Markovic wouldn't be
caught dead

55:19.541 --> 55:21.041
in the Teremok Inn.

55:21.125 --> 55:24.416
- He is. And he is most
displeased.

55:26.416 --> 55:28.458
You should not have messed with
me.

55:28.541 --> 55:29.791
Now you have to answer him.

55:34.000 --> 55:35.416
- I guess I should get ready.

55:37.291 --> 55:39.916
[ominous music]

55:43.750 --> 55:48.583
