55:48.666 --> 55:51.041
[gun fires]

55:52.416 --> 55:55.416
[suspenseful music]

56:04.625 --> 56:08.416
[device clicks and beeps]

56:08.500 --> 56:11.166
[device clicks and beeps]

56:11.250 --> 56:14.166
[device clicks and beeps]

56:14.250 --> 56:15.416
[device clicks and beeps]

56:15.500 --> 56:17.416
