56:26.166 --> 56:28.000
[muffled groans]

56:35.625 --> 56:37.958
Anyone messes with you...

56:38.041 --> 56:39.625
...kick 'em in the balls.

56:39.708 --> 56:43.666
- I love you.
- I love you, too.

57:10.166 --> 57:14.958
[suspenseful music]

57:15.041 --> 57:17.291
- Guys, hide, hide!

57:19.166 --> 57:22.000
[whistling music]

57:44.791 --> 57:46.250
