- Send help!

58:11.750 --> 58:13.666
We're at Teremok Inn.
[switch clicks]

58:13.750 --> 58:14.958
Hello?

58:15.041 --> 58:15.916
Hello, we need help!

58:17.125 --> 58:18.208
[Princess squeals]

58:18.291 --> 58:19.416
[Princess squeals]

58:19.500 --> 58:21.833
[Princess grunts]

58:21.916 --> 58:24.166
[Princess grunts]

58:24.250 --> 58:27.333
[Princess grunts]

58:27.416 --> 58:28.958
[Princess grunts]
- [growls] Stop it.

58:29.041 --> 58:30.333
[Princess gasps]

58:30.416 --> 58:32.541
