58:42.416 --> 58:43.458
[Princess grunts]

58:43.541 --> 58:44.458
- Chloe!

58:44.541 --> 58:45.541
[ballerinas clamoring]

58:45.625 --> 58:48.541
- [henchmen] There! There!
There!

58:50.250 --> 58:51.458
- There's more! There's more!

58:51.541 --> 58:54.208
[henchmen clamoring]

58:54.291 --> 58:57.666
[ballerinas gasping]

58:59.416 --> 59:00.666
[ballerinas gasping]

59:00.750 --> 59:03.041
