indistinctly]

59:03.125 --> 59:06.291
- [Grace] Why the fuck are we
back here?

59:08.041 --> 59:11.416
[ballerinas clamoring]

59:12.291 --> 59:14.333
- Okay. Hey, hey, hey.

59:14.416 --> 59:17.833
My friends and I, we
just wanna leave. Okay?

59:17.916 --> 59:20.333
No one has to get hurt.

59:20.416 --> 59:21.916
Guys, the door, the door.

59:22.000 --> 59:22.958
Go, go, go, go!

59:23.041 --> 59:26.541
[dramatic music]

59:26.625 --> 59:28.958
If we want to survive, we have
to do this as a team.

59:29.041 --> 59:32.000
[dramatic music]

59:35.250 --> 59:37.541
The only way out is together.

59:39.916 --> 59:42.708
First positions. Six, seven,
eight.

59:42.791 --> 59:47.791
