- I'm fine.

01:01:15.500 --> 01:01:16.416
- Peel off!

01:01:18.875 --> 01:01:21.291
[man shouts]

01:01:21.375 --> 01:01:22.208
[man shouts]

01:01:22.291 --> 01:01:23.458
[grunts]

01:01:23.541 --> 01:01:24.958
[man grunts]

01:01:25.041 --> 01:01:27.083
[man grunts and thuds]

01:01:27.166 --> 01:01:29.708
[man shouts]

01:01:29.791 --> 01:01:30.750
- Ow!

01:01:34.166 --> 01:01:35.708
[man gasps]

01:01:35.791 --> 01:01:36.666
[ballerina grunts]

01:01:36.750 --> 01:01:39.791
[man grunts and thuds]

01:01:44.666 --> 01:01:47.166
[man grunts]

01:01:49.166 --> 01:01:51.208
[Princess grunts]

01:01:51.291 --> 01:01:52.166
[man grunts]

01:01:52.250 --> 01:01:54.791
[Princess grunts]

01:01:54.875 --> 01:01:56.208
[man grunts]

01:01:56.291 --> 01:01:57.416
[Princess shouts]

01:01:59.875 --> 01:02:01.166
[man grunts]

01:02:02.041 --> 01:02:03.708
[Princess grunts]
[man shouts]

01:02:03.791 --> 01:02:07.166
[Chloe panting and thuds]

01:02:08.416 --> 01:02:09.458
- [Zoe] [shouts] Chloe!

01:02:09.541 --> 01:02:11.416
[fighters clamoring]

01:02:17.666 --> 01:02:19.083
[Chloe grunts]

01:02:19.166 --> 01:02:21.333
[man shouts]

01:02:21.416 --> 01:02:25.166
[man grunts and shouts]

01:02:26.041 --> 01:02:27.458
[Chloe grunting]

01:02:27.541 --> 01:02:30.041
[Zoe gasping]

01:02:30.916 --> 01:02:33.333
[Artyom grunts]

01:02:33.416 --> 01:02:36.666
[Chloe panting]

01:02:36.750 --> 01:02:39.833
["The Nutcracker" continues]

01:02:39.916 --> 01:02:42.291
You're not cute anymore.

01:02:42.375 --> 01:02:45.041
