[ballerinas shout]

01:03:02.625 --> 01:03:08.583
[muffled sounds]

01:03:08.666 --> 01:03:11.166
[Zoe gasps]

01:03:17.166 --> 01:03:19.666
[gun firing]

01:03:34.750 --> 01:03:37.500
[device beeping]

01:03:38.416 --> 01:03:43.416
[device beeping]

01:03:49.375 --> 01:03:51.916
[men groaning]

01:03:56.541 --> 01:03:59.541
[ballerinas panting]

01:04:01.916 --> 01:04:02.833
- [Princess] Okay.

01:04:02.916 --> 01:04:05.541
- Quick! Right there.

01:04:05.625 --> 01:04:07.291
We can go out that window.
Come on!

01:04:08.916 --> 01:04:11.791
[intense music]

01:04:22.416 --> 01:04:24.416
- Shit for brain. Give me the
gun!

01:04:24.500 --> 01:04:25.625
Quick! Gun!

01:04:27.750 --> 01:04:29.291
- Oh.
[ballerinas clamoring]

01:04:29.375 --> 01:04:30.208
- Go, go, go!

01:04:30.291 --> 01:04:32.250
Go, Grace, go! Come on.

01:04:35.541 --> 01:04:37.041
[Saber grunts]

01:04:37.125 --> 01:04:39.583
[Princess grunting]

01:04:39.666 --> 01:04:40.791
- Hello again.

01:04:43.583 --> 01:04:44.708
[Princess grunts]

01:04:44.791 --> 01:04:46.541
[Princess grunts]

01:04:48.666 --> 01:04:50.416
[panting]

01:04:50.500 --> 01:04:51.541
[gun fires]

01:04:53.416 --> 01:04:54.875
[Princess grunts]

01:04:58.375 --> 01:05:00.458
- We got it!

01:05:00.541 --> 01:05:01.458
- Just go, okay?

01:05:01.541 --> 01:05:04.458
I'm right behind you. Go!
[panting]

01:05:04.541 --> 01:05:05.666
- I'll wait for you.

01:05:07.625 --> 01:05:11.083
[footsteps tapping]

01:05:11.166 --> 01:05:12.708
[ominous music]

01:05:12.791 --> 01:05:13.666
- Impressive.

01:05:16.291 --> 01:05:17.916
Brava, my girl.

01:05:29.541 --> 01:05:31.791
[gun clicks]

01:05:31.875 --> 01:05:34.708
[gun clicking]

01:05:34.791 --> 01:05:37.666
Your gun is dry. You have no
moves left.

01:05:39.291 --> 01:05:40.166
[Bones growls]

01:05:41.041 --> 01:05:42.083
[Bones panting]

01:05:42.166 --> 01:05:43.375
Did I not mention?

01:05:44.166 --> 01:05:46.166
Fake leg.

01:05:54.666 --> 01:05:56.041
- Ha!

01:05:56.125 --> 01:05:57.666
Now that's what's up.

01:05:57.750 --> 01:06:00.166
[Bones grunts]

01:06:00.250 --> 01:06:02.791
- You know I have your
father to thank for this leg.

01:06:04.166 --> 01:06:06.458
- What? Papa?

01:06:06.541 --> 01:06:07.750
[gun fires]
[Pasha shouts]

01:06:08.541 --> 01:06:10.208
[Pasha groans]

01:06:10.291 --> 01:06:12.458
- Shh. It is done.

01:06:12.541 --> 01:06:14.458
I cannot have you running
back to your father

01:06:14.541 --> 01:06:15.833
the minute he arrives.

01:06:15.916 --> 01:06:19.916
You see, I crave his audience.

01:06:23.166 --> 01:06:25.791
[Pasha groans]

01:06:28.250 --> 01:06:30.791
- [Pasha] You are crazy, Devora!

01:06:32.416 --> 01:06:34.833
My father will kill you!

01:06:34.916 --> 01:06:38.291
[ominous music continues]

01:06:39.541 --> 01:06:42.666
[ballerinas panting]

01:06:42.750 --> 01:06:44.833
- [Princess] Holy crap.

01:06:44.916 --> 01:06:47.333
Come on, Bones. Where are you?

01:06:47.416 --> 01:06:50.083
- [Grace] I think I cut myself
on glass.

01:06:50.166 --> 01:06:52.416
- [Zoe] How could you leave her?

01:06:52.500 --> 01:06:54.333
- [Princess] I... She was right
behind me.

01:06:54.416 --> 01:06:57.541
- [Zoe] Come on.

01:06:57.625 --> 01:07:00.916
- [Grace] [grunts] Oh.

01:07:01.000 --> 01:07:03.208
- [Zoe] What are
we gonna do about Bones?

01:07:03.291 --> 01:07:04.416
- [Princess] Okay, relax.

01:07:04.500 --> 01:07:07.375
You guys
hide and I'll save her ass.

01:07:11.416 --> 01:07:13.541
- [Devora] Your friends have
left you for dead.

01:07:14.625 --> 01:07:16.666
There's no one here to hold your
hand.

01:07:19.666 --> 01:07:23.791
You know, I went to my
first audition on my own.

01:07:23.875 --> 01:07:25.000
I was eight.

01:07:26.125 --> 01:07:28.666
Like you, I would not let fear
stop me.

01:07:28.750 --> 01:07:30.208
- [muffled] We are not alike.

01:07:30.291 --> 01:07:34.166
- My debut role was to
be the Sugar Plum Fairy.

01:07:37.125 --> 01:07:39.000
But did I dance it?

01:07:40.625 --> 01:07:41.541
No.

01:07:44.875 --> 01:07:48.208
My papa, he racked up
debt with the wrong man.

01:07:48.291 --> 01:07:50.416
He figured at worst he'd kill
him, but...

01:07:52.541 --> 01:07:55.375
He was crueler than my
papa had anticipated.

01:07:57.416 --> 01:08:00.291
When Papa couldn't pay,
Markovic,

01:08:02.041 --> 01:08:04.375
he didn't take Papa's leg.

01:08:06.000 --> 01:08:06.916
He took mine.

01:08:08.916 --> 01:08:10.791
I would never dance again.

01:08:14.041 --> 01:08:16.166
I kept Lothar's son close,

01:08:16.250 --> 01:08:19.666
hoping one day my opportunity
would come.

01:08:22.041 --> 01:08:24.791
[dramatic music]

01:08:41.041 --> 01:08:45.000
[Devora] One last dance.

01:08:55.041 --> 01:08:57.500
[bus driver snoring]

01:08:58.625 --> 01:08:59.457
[vehicles roaring]

01:08:59.541 --> 01:09:00.541
[bus driver gasps]

01:09:06.500 --> 01:09:09.916
[dramatic music continues]

01:09:35.666 --> 01:09:36.916
[Devora gasps]

01:09:45.916 --> 01:09:48.041
[Bones grunting]

01:09:48.125 --> 01:09:49.957
[device beeping]

01:09:50.041 --> 01:09:52.332
[Bones grunting]

01:09:52.416 --> 01:09:53.832
[light suspenseful music]

01:09:53.916 --> 01:09:57.833
[Doktor speaking French]

01:09:57.916 --> 01:09:59.041
- It means,

01:09:59.125 --> 01:10:01.791
[Bones yelling]

01:10:03.125 --> 01:10:05.250
your struggle looks ridiculous.

01:10:09.041 --> 01:10:10.916
You look like angry little goat.

01:10:11.750 --> 01:10:14.666
[Bones grunting]

01:10:14.750 --> 01:10:16.791
[Bones sobbing]

01:10:16.875 --> 01:10:18.291
- Please stop, stop!

01:10:21.291 --> 01:10:22.208
Stay away from me!

01:10:22.291 --> 01:10:23.791
- Right.

01:10:23.875 --> 01:10:25.666
[Bones grunting]

01:10:25.750 --> 01:10:27.458
- No!

01:10:27.541 --> 01:10:29.541
- Let me make you more
comfortable.

01:10:29.625 --> 01:10:31.041
- Stay away from me!

01:10:32.041 --> 01:10:33.166
No!

01:10:33.250 --> 01:10:34.958
[Bones grunting]

01:10:35.041 --> 01:10:36.583
Let go, let go, let go!

01:10:36.666 --> 01:10:39.375
[Bones panting]

01:10:42.041 --> 01:10:43.291
No!

01:10:43.375 --> 01:10:45.333
No, no, no, no, no, no!

01:10:45.416 --> 01:10:47.541
[light suspenseful music
continues]

01:10:47.625 --> 01:10:48.875
No, no, no, no!

01:10:53.041 --> 01:10:55.791
[Bones laughing]

01:10:57.625 --> 01:10:59.541
Are you kidding me?

01:10:59.625 --> 01:11:01.125
My toenails break all the time.

01:11:02.041 --> 01:11:03.958
And you know what I do?

01:11:04.041 --> 01:11:05.458
I peel them off,

01:11:05.541 --> 01:11:07.416
I put a smile on my face and I
dance,

01:11:08.750 --> 01:11:11.333
because I'm a
balle-fucking-rina!

01:11:11.416 --> 01:11:14.125
[dramatic music]

01:11:22.375 --> 01:11:23.333
- Bones?

01:11:23.416 --> 01:11:26.666
[light dramatic music]
Oh my God!

01:11:28.541 --> 01:11:30.291
Bones, it's me, I'm here, I'm
here.

01:11:30.375 --> 01:11:31.208
[Princess screaming]

01:11:31.291 --> 01:11:33.333
- [Pasha] Please help me.

01:11:33.416 --> 01:11:36.458
Devora's crazy! She trapped me
in here!

01:11:36.541 --> 01:11:37.958
[Pasha moans]

01:11:38.041 --> 01:11:38.916
- Okay, okay. Just keep going.
Just keep going.

01:11:39.000 --> 01:11:40.958
- [Pasha] Help me! [yells]

01:11:41.041 --> 01:11:43.916
[suspenseful music]

01:11:50.500 --> 01:11:54.250
[suspenseful music continues]

01:12:02.291 --> 01:12:05.625
[light suspenseful music]
[Princess panting]

01:12:07.125 --> 01:12:08.791
- Where the hell was this
earlier?

01:12:14.291 --> 01:12:19.166
[engines revving]
[suspenseful music]

01:12:25.041 --> 01:12:28.791
[suspenseful music continues]

01:12:32.125 --> 01:12:34.541
- [Devora] Hello, Lothar.

01:12:34.625 --> 01:12:37.625
- Why are you answering Pasha's
phone?

01:12:38.666 --> 01:12:40.958
Put my son on the line.

01:12:41.041 --> 01:12:44.833
- [Devora] You don't remember
me, do you, Mr. Markovic?

01:12:44.916 --> 01:12:46.958
If you want to see your son
again,

01:12:47.041 --> 01:12:48.666
you better come and get him.

01:12:51.750 --> 01:12:54.541
[Pasha grunting]

01:13:03.916 --> 01:13:06.708
[saw whirring]
[suspenseful music]

01:13:06.791 --> 01:13:08.458
[Bones panting]

01:13:08.541 --> 01:13:10.166
[Bones yelling]

01:13:10.250 --> 01:13:11.958
- No, no, no!

01:13:12.041 --> 01:13:13.958
Stop, please stop!

01:13:14.041 --> 01:13:16.791
[Bones screaming]

01:13:21.875 --> 01:13:24.791
[Bones panting]

01:13:24.875 --> 01:13:26.958
[light upbeat music]

01:13:27.041 --> 01:13:28.041
- Stay down.

01:13:30.166 --> 01:13:31.125
Wanna duet?

01:13:33.166 --> 01:13:34.416
- Thought you'd never ask.

01:13:36.291 --> 01:13:39.708
[Bones panting]

01:13:39.791 --> 01:13:40.666
[Pasha grunting]

01:13:40.750 --> 01:13:43.958
[light suspenseful music]

01:13:44.041 --> 01:13:46.375
- [Princess] You motherfucker.

01:13:47.416 --> 01:13:52.166
[suspenseful music]

01:13:55.250 --> 01:13:58.041
That's a lot of guns.

01:13:58.916 --> 01:14:01.791
- We need to warn Princess and
Bones.

01:14:06.666 --> 01:14:10.875
- Then I guess we're going back
inside.

01:14:12.416 --> 01:14:16.125
[suspenseful music continues]

01:14:24.041 --> 01:14:26.250
[suspenseful music continues]

01:14:29.291 --> 01:14:31.916
[rapid beeping]

01:14:33.916 --> 01:14:34.791
- C4?

01:14:36.125 --> 01:14:38.083
- I mean, I see at least 16.

01:14:38.166 --> 01:14:40.958
- No, it's a kind of explosive.

01:14:41.041 --> 01:14:42.791
This place is wired to blow.

01:14:42.875 --> 01:14:44.583
Stop talking and run!

01:14:44.666 --> 01:14:46.458
[suspenseful music continues]

01:14:46.541 --> 01:14:49.125
[bomb beeping faster]

01:14:53.541 --> 01:14:54.833
[everyone gasping]

01:14:54.916 --> 01:14:58.416
Guys, this place, this place,
is wired to...

01:14:58.500 --> 01:15:00.166
- Explode!

01:15:00.250 --> 01:15:02.291
- What? Why the fuck are you
back here?

01:15:02.375 --> 01:15:04.041
- To save you assholes.

01:15:08.041 --> 01:15:10.458
[light suspenseful music]

01:15:10.541 --> 01:15:14.083
- [Pasha] No, no, no, no...

01:15:14.166 --> 01:15:18.291
[light suspenseful music
continues]

01:15:32.208 --> 01:15:33.208
[gun clicking]

01:15:33.291 --> 01:15:35.333
[everyone gasping]

01:15:35.416 --> 01:15:38.208
- Give me that bastard.

01:15:38.291 --> 01:15:40.541
- No! Keep her away from me!

01:15:42.416 --> 01:15:45.041
- [Princess] Devora Kasimer...

01:15:45.125 --> 01:15:46.875
We're just like you. We're
ballerinas.

01:15:48.416 --> 01:15:50.166
